at</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1351470/extras/bc33520bc75768a55277ec68a8dec881.poster.avif?t=1750982484\" width=390 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1351470/extras/bc33520bc75768a55277ec68a8dec881.webm?t=1750982484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1351470/extras/bc33520bc75768a55277ec68a8dec881.mp4?t=1750982484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What you can expect:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 50+ playable cards with unique interactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ranked, skill-based matchmaking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Tons of variety and replay value each time you play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collectable emotes to express yourself in-game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Custom character skins and cosmetics to show off your style</p></li></ul>",
